snippet.title: Puzzle Depot gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Push boxes, battle bugs, collect loot, and more!  Puzzle Depot is a puzzle-based adventure game with a retro aesthetic and post-apocalyptic flavor.

Wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3108190/Puzzle_Depot/

Check out the demo and see if you can complete all the optional challenges!
https://laughing-manatee.itch.io/puzzledepot

Puzzle Depot is releasing Winter of 2024 on Steam and itch.io!
